=20

I outlined most of the differences in my previous email.  The packages are =
very similar.

Previously you purchased our Silver Site License which came with 30 FDTD li=
censes and 20 licenses of our other products, MODE, DGTD, HEAT, FEEM, CHARGE=
, MQW, STACK and INTERCONNECT.  You also purchase our  virtuoso interop lice=
nse. The cost was 25,920 USD excluding duties and taxes.

=20

This year we have a 25 Task Research bundle which includes 25 licenses of e=
ach of our products as well as all our interoperability products and cml com=
piler. Each GUI license comes with 4 engines with a 32  core limit each.  Ou=
r products, including our intereroperability products may be found on our we=
bsite,  https://www.lumerical.com/products/  The 1 year cost is 24,800.00 US=
D excluding duties and taxes.

=20

The cost is lower this year than previously.  The main differences are you =
only have 25 FDTD rather than 30.  However, you also have all of our interop=
erability licenses and the cml compiler, previously not  included.

=20

Best regards,

Catriona

